- AirTraf 1.0 Installation			11/21/2002

/* Quick Install guide for installing AirTraf 1.0      */
*-------------------------------------------------------*

@) Building all at once
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. from the airtraf main directory, change into src directory.
2. Run 'make all' to get a fresh compilation.

@) Installing
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. also from the src directory, do 'make install'

@) Running
~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. run 'airtraf' and it should auto-configure & run.


That's it!

- Elixar Team
support@elixar.com
